        {
          "lang": "zh-TW",
          "lang_word": "noise",
          "definition": "n. 噪音、喧鬧聲  v. 談論、流傳（多用以=noise about/abroad）"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "The construction site next door makes a terrible noise every morning.",
